Q. Create a user named kareem on App Server 2 in Stratos Datacenter. Set the expiry date to 2024-04-15, ensuring the user is created in lowercase as per standard protocol.
Sol. 1. Connect to App Server
          - ssh username@ip
     2. Create the user with expiry date
          - sudo useradd -s 2024-04-15 kareem
     3. Verify the user
          - sudo chage -l kareem
